copyBlock.cwc:
Lightweight Strollers

If you need to carry your stroller up and down stairs or onto public transit, having one that's lightweight and portable can be very helpful.

Many lightweight strollers are umbrella strollers, which have hooked handles and fold up compactly, making them easy to stow in the trunk of your car. Most don't recline fully or offer full neck and back support, so they're best for older babies and toddlers who can sit unassisted. However, you will find some lightweight strollers for newborns as well.

Although the lightest strollers often don't have as many amenities as heavier models, there are some lightweight strollers with ample storage space and features like cup holders and sun shades. Other common features include locking swivel wheels and one-step fold, which allows you to open and break down the stroller quickly and easily, sometimes with one hand.

With a wide selection of strollers and other baby gear at Every Day Low Prices, Walmart has you covered. Save money. Live better.
